    "body": "It turns out there is no test currently to check that the RPC server does not time out under load. With \"load\" I mean a flood of trivial payloads. That is, the only work needed is JSON encoding and decoding of (let's say) a block of data of 2 MB or so. This may take a few milliseconds, but should never take more than a few seconds.\r\n\r\nSo add a test for this.",
